{"tid":526984,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【當更警加一分】警隊總電訊工程師涉使用虛假文件下月再訊","createTime":"2018-01-12T07:46:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-12T09:47:55.000Z","uid":11001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d924fd1c47a1b8677e44d92ad51bb18fc3d9d64c","tid":526984,"uid":11001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T07:46:46.000Z","msg":"一名警務處總電訊工程師涉虛報為單身，及假稱太太沒有接受任何房屋津貼，被控一項代理人意圖欺騙其主事人（即香港特別行政區政府）而使用虛假文件，案件今於東區裁判法院提堂。辯方申請押後答辯，以待被告索取法律意見。官准案件押後至2月12日再訊，其間被告獲准以1萬元保釋，及不得與2名控方證人聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n控罪指，報稱為警務處總電訊工程師的黃振球（58歲），作為港府代理人，於1997年9月8日使用一份「有關公務員/其配偶已享用的房屋福利及與房屋有關連福利的聲明書」文件，意圖欺騙主事人。<br />\n<br />\n據悉該份文件除了對主事人有利害關係之外，黃振球更在要項上載有虛假、錯誤或欠妥的陳述，即被告報稱是單身，配偶並沒有接受任何購屋資助，及他明知該文件是意圖用以誤導港府。<br />\n<br />\n創科局剛成立時，有傳黃振球將會擔任創科局副局長，但因家庭問題放棄副局長一職，及後由時任數碼港技術總監鍾偉強頂上。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180112/s00001/1515735320477\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180112%2Fs00001%2F1515735320477&d=aeR6LJvgMoWyvzS47HCOyQhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=5a05e7a2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180112%2Fs00001%2F1515735320477&h=b091c1fa\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180112/s00001/1515735320477</a>"},{"pid":"7e52e6739e0379181ab05f07ff30560a94934af7","tid":526984,"uid":11001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T09:39:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b00c823ee0c4193c9e8b91a5e9f745ab008800c","tid":526984,"uid":35656,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T09:42:19.000Z","msg":"工程狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"811b00a564984c50516e27622c2762305369f02a","tid":526984,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T09:43:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35b3ffd46a2d2d139c050119960a3d8d51d1fccb","tid":526984,"uid":2442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T09:47:55.000Z","msg":"啫係唔係警察？"}]}